=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T07:57:47.000Z","msg":"早知「唔小心」穿心刀插幾件警犬認誤殺好過"},{"pid":"b9e645348c737f603c9bfa559c206465531b2f09","tid":700177,"uid":36551,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"d72095d192a067de4267bb93cadb9da35daa9ec2","tid":700177,"uid":50595,"like":67,"dislike":0,"score":67,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T07:08:39.000Z","msg":"香港法律 得淡笑<br />\n一刀刺穿心都可以判誤殺<br />\n撞死人幾個月<br />\n醉酒撞的士五個人死都唔使終身停牌<br />\n巴士跌落橋死二十個判幾年<br />\n掟舊磚六年 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T08:10:41.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】○三年七月屯門公路發生二十一死奪命車禍，被判囚一年半的貨櫃車司機李秋榮昨在上訴庭上訴得直，撤銷一項危險駕駛，改判較輕的不小心駕駛罪，並判囚五個月，由於他已服刑逾七個月，遂獲當庭釋放，兩年停牌令則維持。李秋榮離開法院時表示裁決公道，但對車禍死傷者感到遺憾及難過。　記者：陳曉薇<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20060221/5674029\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20060221%2F5674029&d=m9abxLoKsYMdVqo9ZEqPsMP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=a183f08a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20060221%2F5674029&h=f0349327\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20060221/5674029</a><br />\n<br />\n幾年都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 死廿一人坐七個月咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nCut綫迫架巴士落橋都可以上訴拗到變無心之失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再黎一單，超標三倍醉駕六條人命，又點判？<br />\n<br />\n導致六人死亡的羅少權，於慘劇發生接近一年後，被控誤殺及危險駕駛導致他人死亡罪，被判入獄六年及吊銷駕照，需重新考牌才可駕駛。惟家屬認為判刑太輕，律政司於一一年上訴，最終維持六年監禁，但加判停牌至八年。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20140323/mobile/odn-20140323-0323_00176_097.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F201403